data.description: This exceptional move-in-ready 3 bedroom 2 bath home with split floor plan sitting on 1 FULL ACRE is a MUST SEE! Tile flooring throughout the main living area, cathedral ceilings with decorative plant shelves, open concept design, solid wood cabinetry, granite countertops in the kitchens & baths. Sliding glass door give way to a big screened lanai with ceiling fan and large back yard with fruit trees, irrigation system, fire pit, trampoline, and plenty of room for a pool! half acre is fenced in. The screened in front porch offers wonderful outdoor living and updated landscaping, great curb appeal making this house a home!
